      <h1 class='title'>International Labour Organisation Conference 2002</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 15 July 2003 vol 409 c24WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_24ws' title='Col. 24WS &mdash; HC Deb 15 July 2003 vol 409 c24WS' name='column_24ws' href='#column_24ws' rel='bookmark'>24WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0409P0-02353'>
        <a name='S6CV0409P0_20030715_CWS_26'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-chris-pond' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0409P0_20030715_CWS_26' title='Link to this speech by Mr Chris Pond' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-chris-pond" title="Mr Chris Pond">The Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Mr. Chris Pond)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0409P0-02353">The 90th Session of the International Labour Conference 2002 adopted a new protocol to the Occupational Safety and Health Convention 1981 (No. 155) and Recommendation 193 and Recommendation 194 on Promotion of Cooperatives. My right hon. Friend the Secretary of State has today laid before Parliament a White Paper entitled "International Labour Conference, proposed action on one Protocol and two Recommendations adopted at the 90th Session of the International Labour Conference 2002 (Cm 5870)", copies of which have been placed in the Library.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
